      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this absolute beauty. It has been my pride and joy, and honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve been super meticulous with it\u2014not a single scratch or speck of dust anywhere. It drives like a dream and the interior is still smelling fresh. I\u2019m really sad to let it go, but I know it\u2019s going to make someone very happy. Come by and take it for a spin, you won't be disappointed!",
